added.title: Working K9 to 5
added.description: Release the hounds! Campers are hunted by a pack of fearsome attack dogs. And one pug.

added.title: Off The Hook
added.description: Things get scary when campers are pulled into a fishhook challenge that pits them against each other AND their worst fears.

added.title: Soar Losers
added.description: Only 3 campers remain and if any of them live through the final challenge they might win the 1 million dollars Chris promised them. But on Total Drama Island promises are a lot like bones; they're often broken.

added.title: Meet the Victims
added.description: Chris welcomes 16 new campers back to the original island and divides them into two teams who face-off in a blindfolded challenge that's sure to cause pain.

added.title: Pirates of the Cabbagean
added.description: Our two teams go to war, firing cabbages from cannons at each other from their respective pirate ships. The first team to sink the other will be the winner, but someone takes a very personal interest in one specific target.

added.title: The Limo
added.description: To help distract Panda from his girl problems, Grizz and Ice Bear treat him to a ride in a limo.

added.title: More Everyone's Tube
added.description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

added.title: Money Man
added.description: The Bears help Chloe present her project for a college science contest. But Chloe's rival makes things difficult.

added.title: Rescue Ranger
added.description: Tabes helps the Bears rescue Charlie after he gets captured by a villainous game hunter.

added.title: El Oso
added.description: In a flashback to long ago, Charlie has an adventure in the Mexican desert.

added.title: Cosmic Bupkiss
added.description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

added.title: Radio Silence
added.description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

added.title: Director's Cut
added.description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

added.title: Haunted Campfire
added.description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

added.title: I Heart Heartforde
added.description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

added.title: The Forge of Creation
added.description: Professor Paradox holds the key to stopping Aggregor from tapping into the limitless power of Alien X.

added.title: Practice Makes Purple
added.description: When Vivie discovers she's not amazing at soccer the first time she tries, she thinks she'll never be good at it. Barney creates fantastiical practice drills to help Vivie learn how practice can help her get better.

added.title: Team Mateys
added.description: When Mel's pretzel is eaten by a pigeon, Barney creates a high-seas adventure to find another, but it goes awry when Captain Mel doesn't listen to her crew. Mel realizes it's important to listen to others when you're working as a team.

added.title: Save the Garden
added.description: Determined to save the community garden, Barney and the kids go on a magical adventure where they become butterflies, and help a little ladybug with a big problem. They ultimately learn that doing small things can affect big change!

added.title: Dances with Goblins
added.description: David can't agree on what to play, so the kids end up playing different games. Barney has a hard time keeping up with both games. Silly chaos ensues, and David is reminded that it's important to consider others' perspectives, too.

added.title: Outer Space
added.description: The Looney Builders build Marvin the Martian and his Martian crew a space station. Marvin soon becomes overwhelmed by his Martian crew's antics and lack of personal space.

added.title: The Great Flying Flea
added.description: The Looney Builders discover Zippy, an acrobatic flea, living on Sylvester's back. They build Zippy a flea circus to try and convince him to relocate and relieve Sylvester's itch.

added.title: The Snuffles
added.description: The Looney Builders are hired to build an outdoor movie theater in the park. Lola is sick, but she doesn't want to admit it and miss out on all the fun.

removed.title: Go Fish
removed.description: While on a fishing trip, the Bears get attacked by a giant legendary fish.

removed.title: Teacher's Pet
removed.description: The Baby Bears escape their hectic lives by attending school.

removed.title: The Park
removed.description: The Bears spend a day at the park. Grizz works out. Panda attempts to sell his artwork. Ice Bear trains some kids.

removed.title: Baby Bears Can't Jump
removed.description: In order to win a pizza, the Baby Bears play basketball against a ragtag gang of kids.

removed.title: I Am Ice Bear
removed.description: After Ice Bear hits his head, Grizz and Panda notice him acting like a different person.
